roval of Gus\' rich father, Esmond Sr., who thinks that Lorelei is just after his money. When Lorelei goes on a cruise accompanied only by her best friend, Dorothy Shaw, Esmond Sr. hires Ernie Malone, a private detective, to follow her and report any questionable behavior that would disqualify her from the marriage.','/xORxfun2s1Gn43nPbYkMpQZZ9sK.jpg','/fDozhst5HVJJcd3BM8ZOsKniO7Q.jpg','1953-07-14',7.3),(760,'The Mad Adventures of Rabbi Jacob','In this riot of frantic disguises and mistaken identities, Victor Pivert, a blustering, bigoted French factory owner, finds himself taken hostage by Slimane, an Arab rebel leader. The two dress up as rabbis as they try to elude not only assasins from Slimane\'s country, but also the police, who think Pivert is a murderer. Pivert ends up posing as Rabbi Jacob, a beloved figure who\'s returned to France for his first visit after 30 years in the United States. Adding to the confusion are Pivert\'s dentist-wife, who thinks her husband is leaving her for another woman, their daughter, who\'s about to get married, and a Parisian neighborhood filled with people eager to celebrate the return of Rabbi Jacob.','/buhxzPfcFKmw0U1rSgLRqh2swnp.jpg','/80dKVpKKxexxoFvpCJayxJ7cDif.jpg','1973-10-17',7.4),(761,'The Wing or The Thigh?','Charles Duchemin, a well-known gourmet and publisher of a famous restaurant guide, is waging a war against fast food entrepreneur Tri- catel to save the French art of cooking. After having agreed to appear on a talk show to show his skills in naming food and wine by taste, he is confronted with two disasters: his son wants to become a clown rather than a restaurant tester and he, the famous Charles Duchemin, has lost his taste!','/w35oEmLCEjzHOqBjG5c3kLTaXEK.jpg','/ywkIu5l3iAgPZvLFEVBDYxLouH8.jpg','1976-10-27',7.2),(762,'Monty Python and the Holy Grail','King Arthur, accompanied by his squire, recruits his Knights of the Round Table, including Sir Bedevere the Wise, Sir Lancelot the Brave, Sir Robin the Not-Quite