nd together to stop the otherworldly threat.','/3RWsSQlqzRjsuqSRmoyggy74UA7.jpg','/wJmWliwXIgZOCCVOcGRBhce7xPS.jpg','2016-07-14',5.4),(43200,'Basilicata coast to coast','A music group and a journalist cross the region of Basilicata by foot to attend a music festival.','/38W3ELhUprf0aTWyviRggCs1Jmi.jpg','/1xbNEW2j5gKgnM6Pdo0VStpOdSN.jpg','2010-04-09',6.3),(43209,'Ong Bak 3','Ong Bak 3 picks up where Ong Bak 2 had left off. Tien is captured and almost beaten to death before he is saved and brought back to the Kana Khone villagers. There he is taught meditation and how to deal with his Karma, but very soon his arch rival returns challenging Tien for a final duel.','/70Ah12u1iP67hzH1RbQrk0fxam4.jpg','/sIVrOJVeLqPz9NwNa0e4FpqJCWK.jpg','2010-05-05',6),(43266,'How Green Was My Valley','At the turn of the century in a Welsh mining village, the Morgans (he stern, she gentle) raise coal-mining sons and hope their youngest will find a better life.','/ucQESsrG63LsA5HD70aaPxEyORk.jpg','/zmYNtzq3B17DSpDYkF3JUHBa8Yx.jpg','1941-10-28',7.2),(43316,'All That Heaven Allows','Two different social classes collide when Cary Scott, a wealthy upper-class widow, falls in love with her much younger and down-to-earth gardener, prompting disapproval and criticism from her children and country club friends.','/zi7AjheNhXdlmORg3kqrFXYrBuA.jpg','/9BZRrJK3iMILX0KP8eLb2E4sPqs.jpg','1955-12-25',7.3),(43347,'Love & Other Drugs','Maggie is an alluring free spirit who won\'t let anyone – or anything – tie her down. But she meets her match in Jamie, whose relentless and nearly infallible charm serves him well with the ladies and in the cutthroat world of pharmaceutical sales. Maggie and Jamie\'s evolving relationship takes them both by surprise, as they find themselves under the influence of the ultimate drug: love.','/rsBFDOVtsVQ76dcOsRMTmREFffV.jpg','/1nXN4e3IoTJD42ci7WHZeI1Cgpm.jpg','2010-11-22',7),(43539,'The Next Three Days','A married couple\'s life is turned upside down when the wife is accused of murdering her boss. Her husband John would spend the next few years trying to get her released, but there\'s no evidence that negates the evidence against her. When the strain of being separated from her husband and son gets to her, John decides to find a way to break her out.','/m3lJ0cuR0EXHSYUqiQsnc6G1pu4.jpg','/rXWk1S0Ka7WtkIbi5grCxaY98Dl.jpg','2010-11-18',7.1),(43549,'The Experiment','20 men are chosen to participate in the roles of guards and prisoners in a psychological study that ultimately spirals out of control.','/dKJM7ASnbe2owv92S4OwtqBG8wl.jpg','/zy6hJYii2PJfMRoUBlULhfuLsgL.jpg','2010-07-15',6.4),(43552,'Vanishing on 7th Street','A mysterious global blackout yields countless populations to simply vanish, leaving only their clothes and possessions behind. A small handful of survivors band together in a dimly-lit tavern on 7th Street, struggling to combat the apocalyptic horror. Realizing they may in fact be the last people on earth, a dark shadow hones in on them alone.','/9ZlBFuDml8aT8b2Gpw43RhUBncg.jpg','/8LkZFmL2UHbmP7UnjlRP5gqvvqh.jpg','2010-09-11',5.3),(43554,'Paparazzi','A  montley group of free-lance photographers are desperate to grab a good shot of a celebrity.','/jNQxBszjZN1TjlfKlPCNVEBEl1q.jpg','/5OKYsiKawqMJ3loEDKQI8EzX6Nx.jpg','1998-12-18',5),(43555,'Body Guards','Fabio Leone and Paolo Pecora are two police officers from Rome, which together with the careless Neapolitan Ciro Marmotta, are fired from the barracks to have scuppered the plan to capture a secret agent.','/nl8pXvWj76utoioM3dr2APUDaBL.jpg','/nfVuyuYz1D7SjVZM8JywVHx8xZL.jpg','2000-12-22',5.1),(43557,'Merry Christmas','Four Italian men are suddenly involved in awkward situations, while they are spending the Christmas holiday, stuck in Amsterdam.','/6tyfdMfmLvPDMto1pKdUtuzN1Ku.jpg','/m2bknlPJiZgNpQoERdYxFLgwgmn.jpg','2001-12-21',5.5),(43593,'Piranha 3D','Each year the population of sleepy Lake Victoria, Arizona explodes from 5,000 to 50,000 residents for the annual Spring Break celebration. But then, an earthquake opens an underwater chasm, releasing an enormous swarm of ancient Piranha that have been dormant for thousands of years, now with a taste for human flesh. This year, there\'s something more to worry about than the usual hangovers and complaints from locals, a new type of terror is about to be cut loose on Lake Victoria.','/r1qHFpAJ1HZZm5CuFHw5zhgufMB.jpg','/aa9aXprkzY2YQeGwvsAzLPV3iEF.jpg','2010-08-20',5.4),(43629,'Doodlebug','In his squalid apartment, a man tries to squash with his shoe an insect of some kind that is moving around the room.','/t1NlvLU5xJamUTPVwnWi2o9nR76.jpg','/cXDFFv6yZNW3vUHOKKUPJNnL0So.jpg','1997-01-01',6.6),(43641,'Superman/Shazam!: The Return of Black Adam','Chosen the world’s protector against the Seven Deadly Enemies of Man – pride, envy, greed, hatred, selfishness, laziness and injustice – young Billy Batson accepts his destiny as Captain Marvel. Battling alongside Superman against nefarious Black Adam, Billy soon discovers the challenge super heroes ultimately face: is it revenge or justice?','/gTPDLj2hltXiw64VArHcLory2oZ.jpg','/3MgwChvi42N1RnhQE9A4pQVHyUY.jpg','2010-11-16',7.3),(43645,'The Little Devil','Father Maurice, a priest living in a residential college for priests in Rome, is called out one day to \"exorcise\" the devil from someone. The devil turns out to be in the form of a fun-loving man called Giuditta. What Father Maurice doesn\'t know is that this type of devil will turn his life around.','/cpoCmsmKGsqxwSRPWFKegZbmoQz.jpg','/eD0RzAVRjNvtMfLRSWMAeMo8Foq.jpg','1988-07-01',6.7),(43646,'The Comics','A few funny little novels about different aspects of life.','/xQuAtOd8huwXZi6IvUvjM5lIHwO.jpg','/7bd4nNtxNMlsJc2ysEJMJ01HY36.jpg','1990-10-28',5.9),(43650,'The Legend of Sleepy Hollow','Washington Irving\'s tale of Ichabod Crane and the headless horseman is brought to life, narrated by Bing Crosby.','/tZtawSPJIMCjXOJrUHOlOjJQf5e.jpg','/6bt8qmhxVsgbxFLQCoAcekdCFiw.jpg','1949-10-05',7.5),(43904,'L\'Atalante','Capricious small-town girl Juliette and barge captain Jean marry after a whirlwind courtship, and she comes to live aboard his boat, L\'Atalante. As they make their way down the Seine, Jean grows weary of Juliette\'s flirtations with his all-male crew, and Juliette longs to escape the monotony of the boat and experience the excitement of a big city. When she steals away to Paris by herself, her husband begins to think their marriage was a mistake.','/eooCQusEINqdpTMBkECHluyurW9.jpg','/qg3PQG6QeFpcg45XhYQpsYcabna.jpg','1934-04-24',7.6),(43919,'Hatchet II','Picking up right where the original ended, Marybeth escapes the clutches of the deformed, swamp-dwelling iconic killer Victor Crowley. After learning the truth about her family’s connection to the hatchet-wielding madman, Marybeth returns to the Louisiana swamps along with an army of hunters to recover the bodies of her family and exact the bloodiest revenge against the bayou butcher.','/sh9aRWXveSCeY2TDgNv3UzXAUb9.jpg','/a8Hh6DIOjPE73Hw5ZihDr3k1JDw.jpg','2010-08-26',5.5),(43920,'Dog Pound','Three juvenile delinquents arrive at a correctional center and are put under the care of an experienced guard.','/mHtx1fTr4xKTXEslALzADa2xlY7.jpg','/uyV9XhPpOE5MsvpTAd9FU585oIx.jpg','2010-04-24',7.4),(43923,'It\'s Kind of a Funny Story','A clinically depressed teenager gets a new start after he checks himself into an adult psychiatric ward.','/l7gkk5K0NnVSqZ0Qr4zkNskH9AC.jpg','/jAIoL0275PFrx9jrmneWAqmBvtD.jpg','2010-10-08',7),(43930,'Tomorrow, When the War Began','Ellie Linton, a teen from an Australian coastal town, leads her friends on an excursion to a camp deep in the woods, dubbed \"Hell.\" Upon their return, the youths find that their town has been overrun by an enemy army, and their friends and family have been imprisoned. When the hostile invaders become alerted to their presence, Ellie and her friends band together to escape -- and strike back against -- this mysterious enemy.','/vdSriqZkUUhEUFvzxtA8GGF67DH.jpg','/pGElUTRxtKWlMciQYFO8dIRDytU.jpg','2010-08-08',6.2),(43931,'My Soul to Take','A serial killer returns to his hometown to stalk seven children who share the same birthday as the date he was allegedly put to rest.','/38zLaycGTVCMyyF9x393ds048JF.jpg','/aPbR3auoJJ7cvOofQGw4NWm7OTf.jpg','2010-10-08',5.5),(43933,'Monsters','Six years ago NASA discovered the possibility of alien life within our solar system. A probe was launched to collect samples, but crashed upon re-entry over Central America. Soon after, new life forms began to appear and half of Mexico was quarantined as an infected zone. Today, the American and Mexican military still struggle to contain \"the creatures,\" while a journalist agrees to escort a shaken tourist through the infected zone in Mexico to the safety of the U.S. border.','/imiBIsvNU3TbMB3sbqKanKODS33.jpg','/mDkqx9HDzVcAVsN7HgNEK2uOzWt.jpg','2010-06-18',6.2),(43935,'Dylan Dog: Dead of Night','Supernatural private eye, Dylan Dog, seeks out the monsters of the Louisiana bayou in his signature red shirt, black jacket and blue jeans.','/mbxu6J4qZ69JWNKITrHiR60IXx8.jpg','/pkB97upmnlTZfB8u1Ff452Ybd7X.jpg','2011-03-16',4.7),(43939,'I\'m Still Here','I\'m Still Here is a portrayal of a tumultuous year in the life of actor Joaquin Phoenix. With remarkable access, the film follows the Oscar-nominee as he announces his retirement from a successful film career in the fall of 2008 and sets off to reinvent himself as a hip-hop musician. The film is a portrait of an artist at a crossroads and explores notions of courage and creative reinvention, as well as the ramifications of a life spent in the public eye.','/yZq3kFveiDtfJpwQTgZwXBxs4aE.jpg','/qJsvyPrmZro8pA7v9ozpuoNmsTQ.jpg','2010-09-10',6.1),(43947,'I Spit on Your Grave','Jennifer is a writer working on a new novel and, needing to get out of the city to finish it, hires a riverside apartment in upstate New York to finish her book—attracting the attention of a number of rowdy male locals.','/2hHkKgw9DW0pX0